<div class="panel panel-default">
  <div class="panel-heading">
    <h1>Fantastic Quiz</h1>
  </div>

  <div>

    <div class="panel-body">

      <% if current_user %>
          <h3 class="main">Welcome!</h3>
          <div class="main">
            <tr><td><p>You now have the possibility to create your own questionnaire and start your own quiz to train yourself.
            </p>
              <p>How to start?</p>
              <ol class="main">
                <li><%= link_to("Create a question", new_question_path) %></li>
                <li><%= link_to("Attach a category", questions_path) %> or <%= link_to("create a new one", new_category_path) %></li>
                <li><%= link_to("Start a quiz", quiz_round_overview_path) %></li>
              </ol>
              <p>Only you have access to delete and change your categories and their related questions!</p>
              <p>Sharing your questionnaire with friends enables them to benefit from your work.</p>
              <p>And of course it works the other way around.</p></td>
              <td><img alt="Rails" src="/images/zeiger.png"/></td></tr></table>
          </div>
      <% else %><div class="main">
          <p>You are searching for an innovative opportunity to test your knowledge?</p>
          <p>You have to learn for a test but no idea how to start?</p>
          <p>We offer you a study platform that gives you the ability to create your own questionnaire.
            Start Q&A session and be hero!</p>
          <p>Share your questionnaire with your friends and give them the chance to be as cool as you!</p>
          <img alt="Rails" src="/images/quiz.jpg"/>
          <h3>Get close to the action! Do your registration now or sign in! </h3>
          <br>
          <div align="center"> <%= link_to 'Sign up', new_user_registration_path, class: 'btn btn-danger' %> <%= link_to 'Sign in', new_user_session_path, class: 'btn btn-success' %> </div>
          </div>
      <% end %>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
